{"name":{"entry":104,"name":"Al-Humazah","meaning":"The Traducer"},"verses":[{"arabic":" وَيْلٌ لِّكُلِّ هُمَزَةٍ لُّمَزَةٍ","translation":"Woe to every (kind of) scandal-monger and-backbiter,","transliteration":"Waylun likulli humazatin lumaza"},{"arabic":"ٱلَّذِى جَمَعَ مَالًا وَعَدَّدَهُۥ","translation":"Who pileth up wealth and layeth it by,","transliteration":"Allathee jamaAAa malanwaAAaddadah"},{"arabic":"يَحْسَبُ أَنَّ مَالَهُۥٓ أَخْلَدَهُۥ","translation":"Thinking that his wealth would make him last for ever!","transliteration":"Yahsabu anna malahu akhladah"},{"arabic":"كَلَّا ۖ لَيُنۢبَذَنَّ فِى ٱلْحُطَمَةِ","translation":"By no means! He will be sure to be thrown into That which Breaks to Pieces,","transliteration":"Kalla layunbathanna fee alhutama"},{"arabic":"وَمَآ أَدْرَىٰكَ مَا ٱلْحُطَمَةُ","translation":"And what will explain to thee That which Breaks to Pieces?","transliteration":"Wama adraka ma alhutama"},{"arabic":"نَارُ ٱللَّهِ ٱلْمُوقَدَةُ","translation":"(It is) the Fire of (the Wrath of) Allah kindled (to a blaze),","transliteration":"Naru Allahi almooqada"},{"arabic":"ٱلَّتِى تَطَّلِعُ عَلَى ٱلْأَفْـِٔدَةِ","translation":"The which doth mount (Right) to the Hearts:","transliteration":"Allatee tattaliAAu AAalaal-af-ida"},{"arabic":"إِنَّهَا عَلَيْهِم مُّؤْصَدَةٌ","translation":"It shall be made into a vault over them,","transliteration":"lnnaha AAalayhim mu/sada"},{"arabic":"فِى عَمَدٍ مُّمَدَّدَةٍۭ","translation":"In columns outstretched.","transliteration":"Fee AAamadin mumaddada"}]}